@NODE About "LW About"


W H A T   I S   T H I S   P R O G R A M   A B O U T 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

LightWalker turns a flat 2 colour IFF picture into a shining 3D object.
The lightsource can be positioned and animated.

Lightwalker is excellent for adding shining 3D effects to:
-logos
-texts
-maps
-buttons
-dividers

The result can be saved in IFF and Anim5 format and is perfect for:
-web publishing
-computer presentations
-video productions


@ENDNODE


